d-style"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/02/01/chinesenyfeast_sq.jpg?t=1296590719&amp;s=11" alt="A feast showcases the influence of Asian culture and cuisine on the Caribbean island."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/02/02/133406659/chinese-new-year-trinidad-style">Chinese New Year, Trinidad-Style</a></h3><p>A feast showcases the influence of Asian culture and cuisine on the Caribbean island.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/26/133213620/groovy-recipes-that-are-so-granola"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/01/25/granolaberry2_sq.jpg?t=1295981523&amp;s=11" alt="The crunchy-sweet concoction that became synonymous with the '60s is back with a twist."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/26/133213620/groovy-recipes-that-are-so-granola">Groovy Recipes That Are So Granola</a></h3><p>The crunchy-sweet concoction that became synonymous with the '60s is back with a twist.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/19/133024115/chowders-are-winners-on-winter-table"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/artslife/food/2011/01/hamandcornchowder2_sq.jpg?t=1295376339&amp;s=11" alt="Not quite a soup or a stew, a true chowder features good stock, salt, starch -- and chunks."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/19/133024115/chowders-are-winners-on-winter-table">Chowders Are Winners On Winter Table</a></h3><p>Not quite a soup or a stew, a true chowder features good stock, salt, starch -- and chunks.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/12/132837211/not-all-biscotti-are-created-equal"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/01/11/chocbiscotti_sq.jpg?t=1294772868&amp;s=11" alt="This baton-shaped Italian cookie should be dense, chunky, dunkable --  and noisy till the end."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/12/132837211/not-all-biscotti-are-created-equal">Not All Biscotti Are Created Equal</a></h3><p>This baton-shaped Italian cookie should be dense, chunky, dunkable --  and noisy till the end.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/04/132627711/the-art-of-the-danish-open-face-sandwich"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/01/03/smorrebrodplatter_sq.jpg?t=1294253413&amp;s=11" alt="&lt;em&gt;Smorrebrod &lt;/em&gt;reflects Scandinavian sensibility: simple food attractively presented with little waste."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/01/04/132627711/the-art-of-the-danish-open-face-sandwich">The Art Of The Danish Open-Face Sandwich</a></h3><p><em>Smorrebrod </em>reflects Scandinavian sensibility: simple food attractively presented with little waste.</p></div></div><p class="more"><a href="http://www.npr.org/series/kitchen-window/">more</a></p></div>

